column1: To identify cytokines that may contribute to the increased survival and growth of lymphomas, the expression levels of a panel of cytokines were screened on CD19 + MACS - purified B cells, using an RPA probe set for IL4, IL5, IL10, IL13, IL15, IL9, IL2, IL6, and IFNgamma.

Rabbit anti - pAkt ( Ser473), anti - pGSK3alpha / beta ( Ser21 / 9), anti - pStat3 ( Tyr705), anti - pStat6 ( Tyr641), anti - pmTOR ( Ser2448), anti - Stat6, anti - Akt, anti - FoxO1, and anti - p27 were purchased from Cell Signaling.
